{"tid":339520,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發奇想]其實政府阻止人們掂毒品其中一個原因","createTime":"2017-07-29T06:47:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T07:34:01.000Z","uid":20538,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"878b29e8e199294f81ac8638b48a0e0d9b03aeab","tid":339520,"uid":20538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T06:47:45.000Z","msg":"人類終其一生大腦只運用了3％～4％，其餘97％左右都醞釀在潛意識的右腦當中，這也是21世紀人類最渴望、需要去開發的。 <br />\n<br />\n大家睇過「露西」嘅都知入面係講一種開發腦力的不明實驗化學藥物，其實佢係無講到明係毒品定咩，不過試想下，如果大麻/LSD可以拎人想到平時想唔到嘅事，做到平時做唔到嘅野，算唔算係開發腦力嘅一種？<br />\n<br />\n利申 樓主無掂任何毒品 亦都無教唆任何人去試 只作討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fbb01bda82926447895eac508a4dd2b600c961d","tid":339520,"uid":43760,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T06:55:28.000Z","msg":"其中一個係唔想更多好似你咁既on9出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c89d86a77c976ffbba5347f18a1f8698e26aa4","tid":339520,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T07:05:22.000Z","msg":"咁多人吸毒<br />\n出咗愛恩斯坦未？"},{"pid":"36b992d8647b18b43f73eff0ad21dd4f93369871","tid":339520,"uid":20538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T07:29:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁多人吸毒<br />\n出咗愛恩斯坦未？</blockquote><br />\n但係好多藝術家有更多嘅靈感喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc71f72d09be1d0accc95580007ea95fa7b96c5","tid":339520,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T07:34:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁多人吸毒<br />\n出咗愛恩斯坦未？</blockquote><br />\n但係好多藝術家有更多嘅靈感喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n藝術家有撚用咩"}]}